text: Cng klaw theid (muhammad) phwk than hen læw michı hrux sung kheruxng yang chiph thi xallxhˌ thrng prathan hı kæ phwk than læw phwk than k thahı bang swn pen thi txng ham (ha rxm) læa bang swn pen thi xnumati (ha lal) cng klaw theid (muhammad) xallxhˌ thrng xnumati hı kæ phwk than hrux phwk than pan tæng hı kæ xallxhˌ
